I can't afford everyone getting injured.

27:12.005 --> 27:14.591
[whispers] I could afford two more people
getting injured.

27:14.716 --> 27:16.551
-Okay.
-[clears throat]

27:17.052 --> 27:18.345
So, what's the plan, Sam?

27:19.262 --> 27:20.138
You know what?

27:21.181 --> 27:23.058
We got four episodes left, right?

27:23.391 --> 27:27.354
Fuck it. No one's watching.
No one cares. Ruth can't even walk.

27:27.562 --> 27:29.648
So, I say we do whatever
the hell we want to do.

27:29.731 --> 27:33.443
Let's just set the weirdos free
and see what the fuck happens.

27:33.860 --> 27:35.320
I hope you guys have fun.

27:35.862 --> 27:37.572
[Sam] Oh, you're not getting out of it.

27:37.947 --> 27:40.116
